    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1903638872" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1903638872" />
    <a title="Rita" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5990294-rita"><img alt="Rita" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1621136170p2/5990294.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1903638872?book_show_action=true">Mar 23, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rita" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rita" href="/user/show/5990294-rita">Rita</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1903638872" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2134119726575111561">I wasn&apos;t really expecting to like this, it being about the Catholic Church and all, but I did. The author does a good job of describing his character&apos;s feelings, and I actually related to father Kennedy (I know that&apos;s weird). It was something about being Irish-American and relating to the neuroses of an Irish family.</span>
  <span id="freeText2134119726575111561" style="display:none">I wasn't really expecting to like this, it being about the Catholic Church and all, but I did. The author does a good job of describing his character's feelings, and I actually related to father Kennedy (I know that's weird). It was something about being Irish-American and relating to the neuroses of an Irish family.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2134119726575111561" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


